---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Header } from '../components/Header';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout
  title="高校情報 - Webツール集"
  description="ブラウザだけで動くWebツール集。タイピング練習・顔モザイク・PDFマージ・タイムスケジューラ・プレゼンガイドなど、授業や学習に役立つツールを無料で公開しています。"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100">
    <Header client:load currentPath="/" />

    <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-16">
      <section class="mb-14 text-center">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">高校情報</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          学習向けツールと業務ツール、サポート情報をカテゴリ別にまとめています。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">STUDY</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <a
            href="/tools/typing-japanese"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-sky-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-sky-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2" />
                <path d="M6 8h.01" />
                <path d="M10 8h.01" />
                <path d="M14 8h.01" />
                <path d="M18 8h.01" />
                <path d="M5 12h.01" />
                <path d="M9 12h.01" />
                <path d="M13 12h.01" />
                <path d="M17 12h.01" />
                <path d="M6 16h12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">タイピング練習</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">ひらがなのローマ字入力を練習するタイピングゲーム。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/study/equation-transformation/"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-500 transition-colors group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M4 19h16" />
                <path d="M8 7h8" />
                <path d="M6 12h12" />
                <path d="M10 4v6" />
                <path d="M14 14v6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">等式の変形テスト</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">等式の変形をランダム出題で練習できる択一式テスト。採点・解説・印刷に対応。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/tools/presentation"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-amber-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-amber-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M3 4h18v12H3z" />
                <path d="M8 20h8" />
                <path d="M12 16v4" />
                <path d="M7 8h10" />
                <path d="M7 11h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">プレゼンガイド</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">タイマー・評価ルーブリック・印刷フォームをまとめた授業用ツール。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/tools/pdf-viewer"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-blue-600/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 transition-colors group-hover:bg-blue-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z" />
                <path d="M14 2v6h6" />
                <path d="M9 15h6" />
                <path d="M9 11h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">PDF参照モード</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">ITパスポート等の試験問題をPDFと照合して学習できます。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/tools/anki"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-green-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-green-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M19 5a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M5 11a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M12 11a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M19 11a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M5 17a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M12 17a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M19 17a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M12 23a3 3 0 1 0-3-3" />
                <path d="M6 8h3" />
                <path d="M15 8h1" />
                <path d="M6 14h10" />
                <path d="M12 20v-1" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">覚える君</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">短答入力×分散復習で効率的に暗記できる学習ツール。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/tools/time-schedule"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-purple-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">タイムスケジューラ</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">円形クロックでタスクを時間配分し、タイマーで進行を管理できます。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">TOOLS</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <a
            href="/tools/face-mosaic"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-indigo-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2" />
                <circle cx="9" cy="9" r="2" />
                <path d="m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">顔モザイクツール</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">画像内の顔を自動検出し、モザイク・ぼかし・黒塗りで加工できます。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/tools/pdf-merge"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-orange-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-orange-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M11 21a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-8a1 1 0 0 1 1-1" />
                <path d="M16 16a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H9a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V8a1 1 0 0 1 1-1" />
                <path d="M21 6a2 2 0 0 0-.586-1.414l-2-2A2 2 0 0 0 17 2h-3a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h6a1 1 0 0 0 1-1z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">PDFマージ</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">複数のPDFファイルを並び替えて1つに結合できます。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">SUPPORT</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <a
            href="/tools/sekigae"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 transition-colors group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M4 20h16" />
                <path d="M7 20V8h10v12" />
                <path d="M9 8V4h6v4" />
                <path d="M9 12h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">席替えアプリ サポート</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">名簿作成から座席配置、席替え、共有までの使い方とFAQを掲載。</p>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/support/feature-request"
            class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all hover:border-sky-500/50 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-500 transition-colors group-hover:bg-sky-500/20">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
                <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
                <path d="M8 9h8" />
                <path d="M8 13h5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:group-hover:text-white">機能リクエスト</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">改善提案や追加してほしい機能をフォームから送信できます。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 py-8 text-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:border-slate-800 dark:text-slate-500">
      <p>All processing is done locally in your browser.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
